works.description: I am a medical teacher and I teach medical students and doctors online on my website at www.DrNajeebLectures.com. Many illegal websites have illegally downloaded my videos from my website and uploaded on their websites. This is very bad for my business because google is sending all my customers to those free website. They even tried creating facebook pages but facebook immediately removed the pages. We will be thankful if google can delete the following links from google search and help us protect our business. We spent hours gathering those links so please delete all. Thank you
